<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang='en'>

	<head>

		{% include './partials/head.njk' %}

		<link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/index.css'>

	</head>

	<body>

		<header>

			{% include './partials/header.njk' %}

		</header>

		<main>

			<div id='cardContainer'>

				<div class='card'>
					<span>STOP SKIPPING.</span>

					<p>
						Ever feel like your favourite tunes are stuck on repeat, even with shuffle mode on? Fed up with	hearing the same
						songs over and over again when you're supposed to be enjoying the randomness of your Spotify playlist? Shuffle mode
						shouldn't feel like a broken record, yet you are stuck in a loop of hearing the same songs again and again.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class='card'>
					<span>START <span>SHUFFLING</span>.</span>

					<p>
						Enter Spluff, your solution to the shuffle struggle. Say goodbye to musical déjà vu and welcome	a fresh listening
						experience. Spluff is the antidote to repetition, intelligently reshuffling	your playlists to guarantee a genuinely
						random and diverse listening experience. Try Spluff	today and change the way you experience your favourite tunes!
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>

			<div id='explanationContainer'>
				<span>HOW DOES IT WORK?</span>

				<div>

					<div class='explanation'>
						<img src='/resources/icons/login.svg' width='24' height='24' alt=''>

						<span>
							<span>Login with</span>
							<img src='/resources/icons/spotify_wordmark_black.svg' width='75' height='22.5' alt='Spotify'>
						</span>

						<hr>

						<p>
							Simply log in with your Spotify account and grant permission for Spluff to view and	modify your public and
							private playlists.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class='explanation'>
						<img src='/resources/icons/shuffle.svg' width='24' height='24' alt=''>

						<span>Shuffle your playlist</span>

						<hr>

						<p>
							Spluff will temporarily remove all songs from your playlist, shuffle them thoroughly, and then add them back in
							one go.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class='explanation'>
						<img src='/resources/icons/play_arrow.svg' width='24' height='24' alt=''>

						<span>Enjoy your playlist</span>

						<hr>

						<p>
							This clever process resets Spotify's shuffle algorithm, guaranteeing a fresh and unpredictable sequence every
							time you hit play.
						</p>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>

			<div id='promotionalContainer'>
				<span>Try Spluff and go back to listening to songs you haven't heard in a while.</span>

				<a class='promotionalLink' href='/playlists'>
					SHUFFLE NOW
					<img src='/resources/icons/shuffle.svg' width='24' height='24' alt=''>
				</a>
			</div>

		</main>

		<footer>

			{% include './partials/footer.njk' %}

		</footer>

	</body>

</html>
